This is where we will keep the history of the system development. We'll identify
the MVP for each major release of the system and track each item as it's 
completed.

Release 1
Focus:  Data model for customer, agreement & account 

MVP:  
1. Create a new Customer record, including basic identification & contact info
2. Create a new agreement
3. Create an account based on the agreement
4. Link the customer to the account

Leverage 'Admin' ui interface

Release 2
Focus:  Testing
MVP:
1.  Add test scripts so that 'python manage.py test' validates the product
2.  All functionality created in Release 1 is tested



Release 3
Focus:  Data model for Transactions

MVP:
1.  Create a cash deposit transaction (as if opening a new account)
2.  Create a cash withdrawl transaction






